videos.description: USC OT Chuma Edoga took a swing at a Utah State defender, which resulted in his ejection from the game in the first quarter.
videos.headline: USC OT Edoga ejected for throwing punch

videos.description: Michael Pittman Jr. blocks the Utah State punt to set the Trojans up on the goal line.
videos.headline: USC Blocks Utah State Punt

videos.description: USC OT Chuma Edoga takes a swing at a Utah State defender and pushes an official after the play was over, which resulted in his ejection from the game in the first quarter.

videos.headline: USC OT Edoga ejected for throwing punch, pushing official

videos.headline: Utah State Interception Stops USC Drive

videos.headline: USC Takes Ball Back With Interception

videos.description: USC QB Max Browne finds Steven Mitchell Jr. in the back of the end zone for a two-yard touchdown reception to extend the Trojans' lead over Utah State.
videos.headline: USC extends lead with Mitchell Jr. TD grab

videos.description: USC WR JuJu Smith-Schuster lays a big hit on Utah State safety Dallin Leavitt that keeps him lying on the field for some time before walking off the field under his own power.

videos.headline: Utah State safety Leavitt gets leveled

videos.description: USC punt returner Adoree' Jackson flies down the field untouched for a 78-yard touchdown to extend the Trojans' lead over Utah State.
videos.headline: USC WR Jackson returns punt 78 yards to the house

videos.description: Kent Myers 6-yard touchdown pass to Wyatt Houston
videos.headline: Utah State gets on the board as third quarter ends

videos.description: USC QB Sam Darnold lasers a 15-yard pass to JuJu Smith-Schuster for the touchdown extending the Trojans' lead.
videos.headline: Darnold fires strike to Smith-Schuster for second TD of game
